title: TTC - History of the United States, 1st Edition (out of print)
description:
The first edition of this lecture series, which are usually very worthwhile. This one is very hard to find, I tried to find it myself after my hard drive crashed, but it wasn&#039;t available anywhere. Fortunately, I managed to track it down to one of my old DVDs.

I tried to tag the individual courses with the people who give the lectures, but I might have made a mistake or two.

No guidebook, unfortunately. If anyone does have it, I would very much appreciate it if it were posted here.
